&lt;p&gt;How would I go about merging the separate inner arrays into one like:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;pre class=&quot;lang-js s-code-block&quot;&gt;&lt;code class=&quot;hljs language-javascript&quot;&gt;[&lt;span class=&quot;hljs-string&quot;&gt;&quot;$6&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-string&quot;&gt;&quot;$12&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;hljs-string&quot;&gt;&quot;$25&quot;&lt;/span&gt;, ...]
